Class RelatedPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseElement
      • ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu.resource.BaseResource
        • ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu.resource.RelatedPerson
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions, Serializable, IBase, IBaseResource

    public class RelatedPerson
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR RelatedPerson Resource (An person that is related to a patient, but who is not a direct target of care)

    Definition: Information about a person that is involved in the care for a patient, but who is not the target of healthcare, nor has a formal responsibility in the care process

    Requirements: Need to track persons related to the patient or the healthcare process.

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/RelatedPerson
